{"tid":1870743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"PPRB江永祥郭嘉銓黃埔「榴槤宴客」 14K殯儀猛人同場","createTime":"2020-02-09T05:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T05:51:01.000Z","uid":179721,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"75272989752c53fa75c1b357033ee19d92d7839a","tid":1870743,"uid":179721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:02:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_724240_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_724240_0&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOs5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=928f6e1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_724240_0&h=d969c48f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_724240_0</a><br />\n<br />\n黑幫14K分「忠」、「誠」、「勇」、「毅」四大堂口，警隊新口號也有強調忠誠勇毅。警黑心思如有雷同，未必是巧合。星期五（7/2）警隊高層在黃埔一間老牌酒家包廂設宴，隔離房竟然坐著14K元老「老漢」門生Peter。武漢肺炎市民不敢外出食飯，全場寥寥可數兩枱客，警黑真的是巧合相遇？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【劉公子專訪●不軌意圖】同性為錢主動埋身 已婚男陪睇醫生陪跑步：我食硬你   <br />\n開香檳狂歡<br />\n<br />\n當日酒樓內電視新聞報道醫護擱置罷工，一間廂房此起彼落傳來歡笑聲，門外寫上摸不著頭腦的名字「榴槤宴客」，但內進的人都是警隊高層，包括謝振中總警司﹑警察公共關係科的郭嘉銓總警司及「Er Er Sir」江永祥高級警司，他們每次進出，均有穿著便服的警務人員陪同，十分講究排場。<br />\n<br />\n部長送了數支香檳入內，隨即又傳來尖叫聲。全民抗疫，警務人員大部分都不戴口罩，郭嘉銓多次進出講電話都不戴口罩，毫無防疫意識。諷刺的是警隊平時出勤卻要蒙面。<br />\n<br />\n至於誰是「榴槤」？酒樓職員三緘其口，有一人肯透露：「O記（有組織罪案及三合會調查科」一早訂咗。」對於其他詳情，一概不肯回答。不過，當晚不見四點記者會常客，O記高級警司李桂華。<br />\n<br />\n然而，穿著便服的兩名警員與酒樓職員談笑風生，似乎早已認識。其中一名猛男更脫下外套展示結實的胸肌，埋單更45度向部長鞠躬，究竟餐飯誰人找數呢？<br />\n14K猛人曾當CID<br />\n<br />\n正當一眾警員言笑甚歡，同場出現14K殯儀猛人Peter。他是14K元老「老漢」門生，幾乎所有社團場合都會見到他的影踪。現年大約70歲，年青時曾加入警隊當CID，後來索性轉行做古惑仔。現事在紅磡開殯儀公司，收入可觀。不過據他身邊的朋友透露，Peter最近患癌，喉嚨和舌頭部位動了手術，暫時不能說話，只能以紙筆代言，亦因此消瘦不少。<br />\n警方︰宴會屬私人性質<br />\n<br />\n本刊向警察公共關係科電郵查詢「榴槤宴客」是誰舉辦？有何目的？是否公費消遣？加上當晚不少警務人員皆有喝酒，宴會後有否繼續執勤？警方只簡短口頭回覆，並沒有正面回應問題︰「宴會屬私人性質，於公餘舉行，並不涉及公務。"},{"pid":"9e30732939f81c11781658e5b810aa1360a5a05a","tid":1870743,"uid":203207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"a5233c4782d578a394bfc21e8042c744f5aecaee","tid":1870743,"uid":28944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"原來肛蛇係十四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b272e2df1e58e441284e36068f8d988b8ab16c8","tid":1870743,"uid":51641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"以為返左80年代"},{"pid":"97dc2cb861e2b0f82a3af11e474af5b8e2cda838","tid":1870743,"uid":99745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca35c00c8f0a8bdde4e73492c6fc3e22f368dad","tid":1870743,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286839f4c5949fab0e2afdc70212281d37394a5e","tid":1870743,"uid":129848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e73c4620f6f68371ee4d34b2a7c619bb82399fc","tid":1870743,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9689bbd6465d6b6ae112713902cc88e534745c","tid":1870743,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:37:13.000Z","msg":"想睇劉公子專訪"},{"pid":"91919c15691550de12887a9e21a8abf98b189bfc","tid":1870743,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:38:19.000Z","msg":"慶功宴？"},{"pid":"9d1c6d19dbf14fd635475fc2786cec4d3786d940","tid":1870743,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:38:25.000Z","msg":"14k猛人江永祥 郭嘉詮"},{"pid":"d25a12885cd9aa75179a7b4f3c64eb50dbd51347","tid":1870743,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:38:46.000Z","msg":"警黑上下一心，誅殺港人"},{"pid":"5f0c8259f48b70403b7e668d4a51a8045853267b","tid":1870743,"uid":257448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c9689bbd6465d6b6ae112713902cc88e534745c","tid":1870743,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:37:13.000Z","msg":"想睇劉公子專訪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c88b8964a83894bb5d9bd9c75881537516b473","tid":1870743,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b272e2df1e58e441284e36068f8d988b8ab16c8","tid":1870743,"uid":51641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"以為返左80年代"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:51:01.000Z","msg":"70年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}